{"TopicId":212360,"ForumId":126,"TopicTitle":"How do I close tutorial window in VAB?","CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-24T17:04:11Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-24T17:04:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just started and clicked on something, and now I have a floating window I cannot get rid of.\u00A0 I\u0027d post a screenshot, but not sure how to do that yet.\u00A0 It happened when I clicked \u0022next\u0022 on the pop-up tutor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: Mananged to get rid of it by forcing a launch and just clicking through all of it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-24T17:07:06Z\u0022 title=\u002202/24/2023 05:07  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 24, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Klapaucius\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"modus","CreatedById":207631,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-24T17:46:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso had this. Yelled at it to go away. Didn\u0027t work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThink I went to the main menu and back to get rid of it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe tutorial paige thing is very annoying.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LameLefty","CreatedById":57336,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-24T21:14:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do we disabled this P.A.I.G.E. stuff entirely? There\u0027s no setting for it that I could see.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-24T21:21:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI read on another forum that you can turn it off when you set up your new mission.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LameLefty","CreatedById":57336,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-24T22:16:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224240695\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212360\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677273672\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181256\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Klapaucius\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n55 minutes ago, Klapaucius said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI read on another forum that you can turn it off when you set up your new mission.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI actually started a new save and didn\u0027t see the option.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhawk","CreatedById":131400,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-24T22:39:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThread moved from KSP 2 Discussion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TCAlex01","CreatedById":226105,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-25T12:45:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224240795\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212360\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677276972\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LameLefty\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, LameLefty said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI actually started a new save and didn\u0027t see the option.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis option you can find only when creating a new campaign\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LameLefty","CreatedById":57336,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-25T13:16:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224241977\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212360\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677329138\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022226105\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TCAlex01\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n29 minutes ago, TCAlex01 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis option you can find only when creating a new campaign\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, \u00A0I figured it out later - \u201CNew User Experience.\u201D \u00A0This should be a toggle in Settings to turn off once the newbs are familiar with things. Or if a KSP vet forgets to toggle it off when creating a new save.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}